snippet.title: We Are OFK - Release Date Trailer
snippet.description:
Out Now on PS5, PS4, Switch & PC 💛 http://ofk.cool/steam 5 episodes & original pop songs from indie pop band OFK: a music biopic series & interactive E.P. about four friends and a cat, dreaming, dating, and paying rent in Los Angeles. 

🎮 Pre-Order Sale ➡️ http://ofk.cool
🎵 Pre-Save E.P. ➡️ http://ofk.cool/presave
📀 Physical Edition & Vinyl  ➡️  https://www.iam8bit.com/collections/we-are-ofk

featuring their new single "Fool's Gold", out August 18!
Written and Produced by - Luna Shadows & Thomas Powers
Performed by - OFK
Mixed by - Beatriz Artola
Mastered by - Jett Galindo
Vocals by - Teddy Dief
